{"product_id":"a-leaf-frankenstein-art-poster-movie-poster","title":"A leaf | Frankenstein Art Poster | Movie Poster","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"1061\"\u003eBring a touch of emotion and literary magic to your space with this beautifully illustrated \u003cstrong data-start=\"813\" data-end=\"849\"\u003eFrankenstein-inspired art poster\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003cbr data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"853\"\u003eUnlike the usual dark interpretations, this artwork captures a rare moment of vulnerability — the creature, chained yet gentle, reaching out with hesitant hope, and Elizabeth responding with quiet compassion.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1063\" data-end=\"1393\"\u003eFloating autumn leaves add movement and symbolism, blending innocence with melancholy and highlighting the fragile humanity within the creature.\u003cbr data-start=\"1207\" data-end=\"1210\"\u003eSoft painterly textures, muted tones, and delicate dialogue create a cinematic storytelling experience that appeals to readers, art lovers, and anyone who appreciates emotional depth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1395\" data-end=\"1573\"\u003ePerfect for bedrooms, study corners, libraries, creative studios, and aesthetic wall setups, this poster brings warmth, narrative, and a deeply human touch to classic literature.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51290318569768,"sku":null,"price":119.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A5","offer_id":51290318602536,"sku":null,"price":79.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51290318635304,"sku":null,"price":149.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13x19\"","offer_id":51290318668072,"sku":null,"price":169.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/11.webp?v=1766381974","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/a-leaf-frankenstein-art-poster-movie-poster","provider